  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a&nbsp;<em>standard action</em>, you can touch an&nbsp;<em>undead</em>&nbsp;creature and infuse it with negative energy. It gains a +1&nbsp;<em>profane bonus</em>&nbsp;on all attack rolls and&nbsp;<em>saving throws</em>, as well as 1&nbsp;<em>temporary hit point</em>&nbsp;per Hit Die and a +2 bonus to its turn resistance. The bonus on attack rolls and&nbsp;<em>saving throws</em>&nbsp;increases by +1 for every 5 wizard levels you possess. These bonuses last for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1 round). The bonuses and&nbsp;<em>temporary hit points</em>&nbsp;are immediately dispelled if the creature is within the area of a&nbsp;<em>consecrate</em>&nbsp;spell. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<em>Intelligence</em>&nbsp;modifier.</p>"
    },
